Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124854,126939}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129442,131903}No, you mustn't be\Nholding that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131903,136157}Evil spirits are in it! The moon's\Nevil spirits are locked in that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136824,139285}The moon's evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139285,142705}You've got to come up\Nwith a better story than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142705,143831}It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143831,148252}If you hold it up to the full moon,\Nthe evil spirits will be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:33.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148670,153216}Stop your babbling!\NThis moon's jewel belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:49.19,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:165144,169190}Steal the Jewel of the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177031,179242}Meimi, my dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179242,180493}Oh, Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180993,184414}Hi. Talk about great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184414,188710}I'm on my way to cover a story.\NDo you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189460,195174}Why should I go with you, when\NI'm not even on the news-writing staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195174,198928}Because you understand\Nmy intellectual reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200179,202640}I wouldn't say that, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202640,204809}Anyway, we're wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204809,208813}Hey, wait a minute.\NSawatari, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209230,210773}That Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210773,213776}Where does he think\Nhe's taking Haneoka to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223411,226289}May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:52.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226289,232128}I came because I wanted to pray,\Nbut I don't know how to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:56.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232503,236215}My name's Mochida.\NThis is rather embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:01.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236215,241095}I used to be a burglar.\NI just got out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241679,243723}A burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:08.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243723,248561}Please don't get me wrong.\NI'm trying to go straight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:14.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,254275}Only thing is, I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254776,258029}Perhaps it would help\Nif you talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258029,260990}All the things I stole
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:27.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260990,267121}were returned to their rightful owners\Nby the police while I was in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:32.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267789,272418}All except one. A jewel which\Ncontains the moon's evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272960,274170}The moon's evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:40.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274879,280426}Right after I stole the jewel,\Nits owner died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:46.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281260,286557}He had no family,\Nand the jewel was forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289101,294732}After that, it slipped past the police\Nand was sold several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:05:00.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294732,300571}I finally located the present owner\Nand asked him to return the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,305535}What did you intend to do with\Nthe jewel when you got it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306577,308871}I want to return it\Nto its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:13.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308871,313251}I mean, I want to leave it\Nat his gravesite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313251,315002}That's very honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315461,319841}That's the only thing\NI can do in atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319841,324720}But the present owner\Nturned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325471,329976}I thought about stealing\Nthe jewel back, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329976,334689}No, you mustn't steal, not after\Nyou worked so hard to reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:39.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334689,339193}You're right.\NStealing it just wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339193,343948}Why don't you pray again and\Nthis time put your entire heart in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343948,348119}Yes, I'll do that.\NThank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348119,350621}By the way,\Nwhere is that jewel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351205,355835}It's called the Jewel of the Moon\Nand is on display at the Space Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:06:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356252,360798}Oh, yes, I've heard it's supposed\Nto glow like the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361924,364760}So this is the Jewel of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367305,369098}It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369098,373936}There's a rumor that the evil spirits\Nof the moon are trapped in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373936,375730}That's just hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376147,380693}I wonder. Still, it is exciting\Nto think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:33.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387617,393915}Look, that's the space stage, made to\Nsimulate the weightlessness in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396125,398628}That planet looks like the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399170,404258}That's a holograph,\Na 3-D picture of the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404258,407345}Rats, I forgot to take pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:52.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408012,412808}Meimi, get closer to\Nthe Jewel of the Moon. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:58.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413309,418314}Yes, two beautiful objects.\NThis will make a nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419941,422777}Wait a minute, don't bother me.\NI'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424487,426238}Like I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426238,427490}A… Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429992,431953}Didn't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.45,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:431953,433454}Photography prohibited{NOTE:撮影禁止}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434205,436916}Never mind that. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436916,438417}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:24.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439543,444382}I'll bet you followed us here because\Nyou got jealous seeing us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444382,447593}Why would I be jealous\Nabout a girl like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447593,450388}Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450388,453307}All right then, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453307,458354}Err, I came here to see how\Ntheir security system is set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458896,461023}The security system?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461023,462817}Please, Mr. Urano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:48.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463401,468322}Please, Mr. Urano. Give the Jewel\Nof the Moon back to me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468322,470741}You must be out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470741,474036}I'd be a fool to give it\Nto a former thief like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474412,478332}Why can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478332,481627}Enough of this!\NThrow him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481627,482837}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482837,487174}Let me go!\NMr. Urano, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:14.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489135,494140}{\i1}I went through the black market and\Npaid a lot of money to get that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494140,496434}{\i1}I'm not letting that thief\Nget his hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496434,500146}{\i1}I'm going to get rich\Nputting it on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500146,502606}Listen, Saruwatari!\NThe trouble with you is…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513492,514952}Are you all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515911,518789}Thank you. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526756,530760}I see. So that's what his motive was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531343,535431}The way things are, Mr. Mochida\Nwill resort to stealing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535431,538976}Let's get that jewel back for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539727,541937}Yes, Seira, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548069,552323}Boy, that Sawatari\Nsure has a big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553908,555367}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:21.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556285,561832}"I'm going to the Space Museum tonight\Nto steal the Jewel of the Moon. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562666,565669}What's going on? Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572176,575763}I wish she'd give me\Nnotice ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580059,583187}Stupid Asuka Jr.\NHe's always interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587358,591070}Hey, Asuka Jr., what's the big rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591070,594615}Get out of my way!\NI can't be wasting time with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599286,601330}It's from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601330,605126}This is the break I've been\Nwaiting for! Asuka Jr., wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609171,613551}Sorry, Ruby. I have a job to do.\NI'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618389,622309}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627231,628315}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630734,631986}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633821,636448}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650045,655885}Still, it does bother me to think\Nthere's evil in that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656677,660598}Oh, Seira,\Nthat's nothing but hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:06.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661140,666312}Yes, but you mustn't let\Nyour guard down. Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666896,669523}Don't worry. I'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671901,675487}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677156,679575}I don't need your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680534,681535}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682745,689251}Even if you don't hire me, the Mayor\Nhas ordered me to arrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692004,693464}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696133,699637}Wow, look at all the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:45.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700346,705601}With equipment like this, St. Tail is\Nno more than a mouse, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:50.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706060,710814}Mr. Urano, this equipment\Nis no match for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:55.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711315,715152}Well, if you're going to insist,\Ndo as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715152,718530}Just don't interfere with our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719782,721367}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721367,723827}Boy, what a grouch!
Comment: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:05.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:725746,725746}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:10.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:730751,730751}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:34.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750854,754775}It's been forced open, but by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761490,765869}Boy, I'm getting old.\NI'm already out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785139,786432}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786432,788767}I thought I saw\Na shadow on monitor A.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788767,790477}You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790477,791353}Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799737,802531}Why, that's Mr. Mochida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803115,807786}I can't let him commit a crime.\NI've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815544,817129}It must have been my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817129,819173}Don't fall apart on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821008,822676}It's St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823802,825679}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:52.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826597,832394}Even the infamous St. Tail couldn't\Nsteal the jewel from this museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843989,845324}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856418,857503}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861048,862966}Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864218,865928}Rats! You're not\Ngetting away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874478,875145}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878941,881068}It's a high electrical current!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889410,891203}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892246,893497}Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898252,899920}Come back here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910139,912558}Snap out of it, Mr. Mochida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916019,919690}Mr. Urano, using high voltage\Nis very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:25.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920649,925529}I will use every means available\Nto protect my priceless display.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:31.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926029,931493}You didn't tell us you hid the jewel\Nand were displaying a holograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931493,932703}That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932703,936957}I'm not so stupid that I'd let someone\Nsteal my jewel so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936957,939751}It sent St. Tail—\NI mean, Holy Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939751,943797}scampering away with her tail\Nbetween her legs. How fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:55.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949344,955309}Damn that Urano.\NHe hid the Jewel of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:16:00.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955642,960272}Mr. Mochida, I promise I'll get\Nthe Jewel of the Moon back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:13.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966904,973118}I can't do my job unless\Nyou tell me where the real jewel is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:19.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973118,979583}Your services are not needed.\NWe can take care of St. Tail ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:26.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979583,986381}Let's go. St. Tail took quite a blow.\NI don't think she'll be back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986381,991512}No, I'm sure she'll return.\NIt's in her nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993805,997226}That's strange.\NMonitor F has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999686,1003690}What's going on?\NThe hologram system's being activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1007945}All the monitors are showing\Nthe hologram system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007945,1009655}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010322,1011406}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013909,1017412}I've got it.\NI know where the jewel's hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017412,1019498}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030050,1032970}Mr. Urano, that moon\Nis the jewel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037349,1041853}Oh, I get it. He hid it\Ninside the holograph image!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044940,1045857}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046441,1049570}St. Tail, I'll get you\Nfor sure tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:35.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051113,1055993}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:43.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057411,1063667}I'm inviting you three\Nto the space station!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080642,1082102}Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082102,1083645}This is some scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:13.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088191,1093030}If I turn the power off,\Nthe anti-gravity field will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093030,1095949}St. Tail, you'll be thrown\Nto the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109838,1111590}Why doesn't she fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113342,1115844}The jewel is mine.\NI'm not giving it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118764,1119348}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126146,1127272}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131485,1133236}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138158,1140160}This couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143205,1145415}It's the evil from the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145415,1148085}No! The jewel is acting as a lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148085,1152839}The moonlight hit it and it's\Ngiving off that blinding glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160347,1161348}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:27.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164810,1167604}I'm taking the Jewel of the Moon\Nback with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168313,1170065}St. Tail, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172359,1174945}Rats! She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:40.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174945,1180617}Don't get depressed. I have a picture\Nof her right here in my camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190460,1193588}I am returning your jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195257,1197968}May you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:07.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200887,1207185}St. Tail, with your help,\NI managed to stay clean. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219322,1222909}We're finally going\Nto uncover St. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228623,1229791}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229791,1232294}I don't remember taking this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:36.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232294,1236089}That's all? After all that talk\Nabout unveiling St. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236089,1237132}You lousy reporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237132,1239634}Shut up, you miserable detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239634,1240927}Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240927,1241803}The same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243722,1246433}If you're so hot,\Nwhy don't you arrest St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246433,1248268}Why, you!
