Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:11.37,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1264284,1271374}I want to become someone today I'm not.{NOTE:今の自分じゃない　私になりたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:20.05,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1272334,1280050}To have courage and never feel down again.{NOTE:二度と悲しくならない心が欲しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:26.59,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1280050,1286598}But tonight somehow everything just feels so well.{NOTE:だけど気分がとてもいい夜は}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:35.31,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1287682,1295315}I wouldn't mind if things stayed that way.{NOTE:ずっとこのままでいたいなんて思う}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:41.94,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1295315,1301947}No matter how you look at the Moon,{NOTE:月がどんな形に見えても}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.45,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1302906,1309454}It's but a dust in a dark, soundless universe.{NOTE:暗く音のない宇宙の塵の中}
